{"tid":1382461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民間發起一人一信 要求機電署無限期暫停水炮車驗收","createTime":"2019-07-29T13:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T08:36:28.000Z","uid":91648,"like":209,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"d447c16a13698036f27fc3bade48c28010b285e1","tid":1382461,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:10:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民間發起一人一信 要求機電署無限期暫停水炮車驗收<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2413616\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2413616&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiicIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=a96290af\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2413616</a><br />\n自從反對逃犯條例修訂後，示威和抗爭活動一浪接一浪，至今已爆發出多次激烈的警民衝突，有聲音呼籲警方應使用水炮車（人群管理特別用途車）。不過由於水炮車的威力可以對人造成很大傷害，網絡作家及評論員林鴻達便發起一人一信，要求<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">機電工程署</span></span>無限期暫停水炮車的驗收工作。<br />\n<br />\n今日有本地媒體引述消息，指警方引入的水炮車，會在今個星期開始實地測試，最快 8 月中可以使用。林鴻達在帖文表示，有關的檢驗工作將會是由機電工程署負責進行，只要機電署完成相關程序，警務處就能夠正式使用，所以他決定去信機電工程署署長薛永恒。<br />\n該封信函大意表示，明白機電署需保持政治中立，但當從香港社會整體利益角度考慮，水炮車可對人生安危造成嚴重禍害。如果機電署停止驗收程序，水炮車便不能出動。相反若完成程序，水炮車有可能造成人道災難，機電工程署將難辭其咎，甚至有可能被國際社會譴責及追究。<br />\n他又指出，香港社會當前最需要的是喘息下來，緩和民間與政府的對峙局面，重塑相對平和的社會氣氛，尋求解決方法。他認為，薛署長無需根據政府行政指引於 14 日內回覆，而如今關鍵就在機電工程署，懇請薛署長三思。<br />\n林鴻達希望網民也能一人一信，所以提供了信函樣本。有網民亦響應呼籲，修改後再寄出。"},{"pid":"f423b6f37c04ed3cb9f05bb146ffb9287d80aa8d","tid":1382461,"uid":108337,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:31:31.000Z","msg":"全機電署都要cc晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa35257324eee1d5faf014c0390a3a04ac403b63","tid":1382461,"uid":281419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:34:05.000Z","msg":"推上黎先"},{"pid":"659683712369069c53329c8fa64801413ab750c1","tid":1382461,"uid":271407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6e910eac1851b85aa1a3c6c70e299cbaab6837","tid":1382461,"uid":281419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:35:34.000Z","msg":"樓主漏左template link<br />\n<a href=\"https://jackyhtlim.blogspot.com/2019/07/LetterToEMSDAlfredSit.html?fbclid=IwAR1qbLmZPkwvPa4ajIg-qEULVkGPJVttzpnA6fRv0aYngpMjf_AbIh2DAfQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjackyhtlim.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F07%2FLetterToEMSDAlfredSit.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1qbLmZPkwvPa4ajIg-qEULVkGPJVttzpnA6fRv0aYngpMjf_AbIh2DAfQ&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiicIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=8bf9b806\" target=\"_blank\">https://jackyhtlim.blogspot.com/2019/07/LetterToEMSDAlfredSit.html?fbclid=IwAR1qbLmZPkwvPa4ajIg-qEULVkGPJVttzpnA6fRv0aYngpMjf_AbIh2DAfQ</a>"},{"pid":"e1f940bf3e278565898cb8b94f5411f75a56b98b","tid":1382461,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:38:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98739682bbcec7539ba5dc68eda76807c7db8dd2","tid":1382461,"uid":281419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:39:38.000Z","msg":"大家send email呀！！！！！<br />\n要幫發夢既手足呀！！！！！"},{"pid":"673b87b0f30311e7bfff586411912f2c2de3a053","tid":1382461,"uid":264369,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:40:09.000Z","msg":"驗收呢家野，承担的責任只係怕收左次貨，老闆夠高級就簽得，乜都阻唔到．政府高層冇一隻唔係狗．<br />\n推呢樣搞noise可以，實用性不大．"},{"pid":"469902a04dbf0902f7abc295063a012fcd9e5d95","tid":1382461,"uid":91648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ec6e910eac1851b85aa1a3c6c70e299cbaab6837","tid":1382461,"uid":281419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:35:34.000Z","msg":"樓主漏左template link<br />\n<a href=\"https://jackyhtlim.blogspot.com/2019/07/LetterToEMSDAlfredSit.html?fbclid=IwAR1qbLmZPkwvPa4ajIg-qEULVkGPJVttzpnA6fRv0aYngpMjf_AbIh2DAfQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjackyhtlim.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F07%2FLetterToEMSDAlfredSit.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1qbLmZPkwvPa4ajIg-qEULVkGPJVttzpnA6fRv0aYngpMjf_AbIh2DAfQ&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiicIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=8bf9b806\" target=\"_blank\">https://jackyhtlim.blogspot.com/2019/07/LetterToEMSDAlfredSit.html?fbclid=IwAR1qbLmZPkwvPa4ajIg-qEULVkGPJVttzpnA6fRv0aYngpMjf_AbIh2DAfQ</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f248dbf7797b7cd26160a3cd97ee2e1a0cf38d2d","tid":1382461,"uid":281419,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:41:16.000Z","msg":"直接擺個template上黎<br />\n自己改姓跟住send出去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n致：<br />\n機電工程署<br />\n香港九龍啟成街3號7樓<br />\n機電工程署署長/總經理 薛永恒先生, JP <br />\n<br />\n電郵：alfredsit@emsd.gov.hk<br />\n傳真：2890 7493<br />\n<br />\n薛署長 台鑒：<br />\n<br />\n要求無限期暫停警務處「人群控制車輛」即水炮車的驗收工作<br />\n<br />\n請恕冒昧致函 薛署長，但基於當前香港局勢的嚴峻，實在有需要向閣下表達關注。<br />\n<br />\n從今日本港英文報刊《南華早報》報導，警務處三部「人群控制車輛」即水炮車將在日內進行最後檢驗，然後就會投入使用 (網上版本網址：<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/law-and-crime/article/3020397/anti-riot-vehicles-equipped-water-cannons-begin-road\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Flaw-and-crime%2Farticle%2F3020397%2Fanti-riot-vehicles-equipped-water-cannons-begin-road&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiicIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=46288a83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/law-and-crime/article/3020397/anti-riot-vehicles-equipped-water-cannons-begin-road</a>)；以本人所知道和了解的政府採購車輛的程序，有關的檢驗工作將會是由機電工程署負責進行，言下之意，只要機電工程署完成相關程序，警務處就能夠正式使用。<br />\n<br />\n明白署長以至全體機電署同僚，須遵守公務員敘用守則保持政治中立，但請 署長閣下清楚明白和知悉是次來函並不是要施加政治壓力、或要求署長以至全體機電署同僚作政治表態，而是正如發起8月2日公務員集會的聲明當中的「脫下職員證及制服後，我們都是香港人」，當從香港社會整體利益角度為基礎、客觀考慮到警務處近月的執勤情況延伸至「水炮車」的出動將帶來何等嚴重的後果，與及以機電工程署的專業知識和經驗更清楚「水炮車」對人命安危的禍害，得盡可能使三輛「水炮車」未能完成政府採購車輛程序，即是基於政府的行政程序使之未能出動。<br />\n<br />\n再次的向 薛署長閣下表明，來函不是要採取政治施壓，而是知道如今的關鍵就在於機電工程署，就只好促請機電署採取適當行動，避免香港社會出現無可挽救的嚴重後果。事實上，客觀而言，並相信 薛署長閣下都會同意，香港社會當前最需要的是喘息下來，緩和民間與政府的對峙局面，以能重塑相對平和的社會氣氛，尋求解決方法。<br />\n<br />\n不過，作為香港市民，亦有責任向 薛署長閣下和全體機電署同僚清楚指出，如果完成檢驗而警務處能夠使用「水炮車」並出現嚴重危機甚至可說是人道災難，機電工程署將難辭其咎，甚至相信要將要面對國際社會譴責、追究的後果。因此，確切地要求 薛署長閣下機電工程署無限期暫停「水炮車」的驗收工作。<br />\n<br />\n同意 薛署長無需根據政府行政指引於十四日內回覆，但不厭其煩的表示「水炮車」將極可能使香港出現無可挽救的嚴重後果，而如今關鍵就在機電工程署，懇請 薛署長三思。<br />\n<br />\n香港市民 林先生<br />\n2019年7月29日"},{"pid":"491935cbdb9e65d1e40ca2c030a13162aa391039","tid":1382461,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"673b87b0f30311e7bfff586411912f2c2de3a053","tid":1382461,"uid":264369,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:40:09.000Z","msg":"驗收呢家野，承担的責任只係怕收左次貨，老闆夠高級就簽得，乜都阻唔到．政府高層冇一隻唔係狗．<br />\n推呢樣搞noise可以，實用性不大．"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:41:28.000Z","msg":"唔做點知有冇效? 你識預知未來?"},{"pid":"00ee26c8641d82b1ebfc79aac6e7756703d93ba4","tid":1382461,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f248dbf7797b7cd26160a3cd97ee2e1a0cf38d2d","tid":1382461,"uid":281419,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:41:16.000Z","msg":"直接擺個template上黎<br />\n自己改姓跟住send出去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal